Fila x One Block Down collection integrates a leopard print motif and the recurring tagline “Ciao Biella,” which hijacks the common Italian greeting to reveal the brand’s origins in Biella, Piedmont, where FILA was founded in 1911. 
The collection is now available online and in our store in Milan and Rome. Photo by @ragazzi.nei.paraggi #fila #oneblockdown
